text: Ulaka () is a small village west of Velike Lašče in central Slovenia. The Municipality of Velike Lašče is part of the traditional region of Lower Carniola and is included in the Central Slovenia Statistical Region.Velike Lašče municipal site A small chapel-shrine in the centre of the settlement dates to 1882.Slovenian Ministry of Culture register of national heritage reference number ešd 26290 ==References== ==External links== *Ulaka on Geopedia Category:Populated places in the Municipality of Velike Lašče
title: Ulaka, Velike Lašče
